snippet.title: POPGOES - Teaser Trailer (Old)
snippet.description:
www.popgoespizza.com

http://gamejolt.com/games/popgoes/64790

Official teaser trailer for POPGOES (Popgoes' Pizza), a Five Nights at Freddy's fan-game made by a small group of teenagers around the world.

POPGOES takes place in the same universe as FNAF, but only takes the first three games into consideration for the plot. In order to fully enjoy what our game has to offer, you need to forget what the fourth Freddy's game told you. 

More details on our GameJolt page. Teasers and gameplay footage / screens will be shown on our website on a weekly basis. Feel free to ask questions in the comments section of any of our pages.

Help us make the best fan-game ever. 

 - Kane
